Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:28.77,lassie episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:83813,88776}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)\pos(320,310)}John's Decision.\NProtect The Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:39.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96659,99537}Hey, Lassie!\NYou look busy as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:41.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100413,101539}Look, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:44.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102081,104375}Right on time today as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:58.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116262,118389}Lassie!\NShe's here, she's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:02.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118640,122393}I wonder how she can tell\Nwhen to pick up John.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131527,133905}What's up, Spinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134530,136866}Everyone left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136866,139077}Why'd you stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:19.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139077,139911}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:27.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141120,147919}I might have to leave\Nthis school soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148127,149337}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:30.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149337,150296}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:35.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151506,155802}So your dad is considering\Nquitting his job at the mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:36.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155802,156803}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156803,159555}He said it's hopeless to keep\Nworking at Wellington Coal Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159555,161724}So he's looking\Nfor work elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161724,163267}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163267,167188}My Dad is doing his best\Nto make work at our mine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:51.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167188,171401}more rewarding and comfortable\Nthan any other workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171401,173903}I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.11,0:02:56.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176114,176906}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179742,181577}I'm so jealous, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:04.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181577,184872}She comes to pick you up\Nafter school every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195466,197093}Dad, I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203933,205268}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206728,209814}There must be something we can do.\NThere must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:33.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211941,213234}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213234,214026}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214026,215611}Ah, it's you, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215611,217113}I'm a bit busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:41.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217780,221284}You promised we'll go fishing\Ntomorrow, since it's your day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221993,223286}– Fishing?\N– Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224162,227415}If you haven't prepared the tools yet,\Nmaybe I could do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227415,229250}Ah! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229250,231002}That was tomorrow already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:52.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231002,232420}Are you busy with work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:56.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232420,236507}No… I just had this pile of books,\Nso I decided to finally read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238384,240845}I'm so sorry, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240845,242638}I forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:03.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242638,243639}That's okay, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:08.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244557,248186}I heard that the Wellington Mine\Nhas ran out of coal, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:13.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250646,253441}What are you saying, John?\NIt's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254108,255151}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255151,256652}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258863,260948}Where did you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261699,263117}From Spinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:26.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263117,266954}His father is looking for another job.\NHe might quit soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268039,269248}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:31.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269248,271959}So he's looking for another job…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271959,273586}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:39.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273586,279467}It is true that we have been producing\Nless coal lately, however…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:44.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279926,284514}So what? If we just dig a little further,\Nwe'll surely find more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284514,286015}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286015,287016}Really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287016,288392}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288392,291687}That's what the manager\Nand all the veteran miners say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:57.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291687,297360}If we search for it the right way,\Nwe'll reach another seam in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297360,298569}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:02.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298569,302156}That's why you were\Nreading all these books.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302156,303783}Do your best, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303783,305326}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305326,308830}We can go fishing when you\Nfind more coal in the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309789,311290}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311624,313626}– Good night!\N– Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313626,316420}Mom's on a night shift.\NLet's go to sleep, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328266,330101}Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330101,331978}Please open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331978,333855}We have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336065,338609}Starting next week,\Noperation will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339068,342738}Do you have any idea when\Ncan we get back to work again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342738,344866}Everyone is going crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344866,346409}We must be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:49.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:346409,349245}Will we receive our salaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:53.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349245,353124}I'll do everything I can.\NThe manager is doing his best, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:57.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353791,357670}Are you sure\Nwe'll find another seam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357670,358629}Of course we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358629,360798}I am very sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360798,363259}What if we won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.25,0:06:04.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363259,364385}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:07.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364385,367889}Drop it. Mr. Carraclough\Ntold us we'd find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:10.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367889,370641}I trust Mr. Carraclough\Nand everything he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:11.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370641,371642}I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:14.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371642,374896}But my family's savings\Nare almost gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:19.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375354,379400}Next week we'll run\Nout of money to buy food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:27.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383362,387867}If it was just a matter of faith,\Nthen we'd all want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394665,396375}Again, it's just soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:38.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396375,398836}What should we do, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409555,411933}Sir, what's your opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:56.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412642,416020}Needless to say, I can't make any\Njudgment from a single sample alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:57.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416020,417897}Nevertheless…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:58.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417897,418898}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:02.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418898,422818}Will we find more coal or not?\NIt's a simple question!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:06.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422818,426656}That kind of analysis\Nis a very delicate subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:09.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426656,429951}Rushing it will only get you\Nresults you can't rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429951,431619}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431619,433287}So it is possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:15.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433829,435331}I can't say anything for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:17.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435331,437333}Please keep digging for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:21.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437333,441420}We can't reach any conclusion unless\Nwe thoroughly examine the soil's condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441420,442797}We will, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449553,451389}Nothing, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:32.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451389,452348}Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455643,458646}If we don't get positive results fast,\Nwe can kiss goodbye to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458646,459563}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460523,463776}For this region, the layer where\Nsensible amounts of coal can be dug up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463776,465611}is this one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:48.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465611,468614}But this indicates that\Nit's a relatively narrow area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468614,469615}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:55.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469615,475079}I simply can't believe that we've already\Ndug up all the coal in this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:59.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475663,479625}I've been mining coal in this mine\Nfor more than 40 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:02.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479625,482837}Something similar has already\Nhappened once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:07.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482837,487550}It was exactly the same.\NIt looked like we ran out of coal to mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:12.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487550,492596}But it was nothing. We struck\Nanother layer, only 5 yards deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:16.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493055,496517}I've also been through this,\Nmore than once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496517,499103}It's reassuring to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:20.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499478,500438}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:23.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500438,503816}I don't want to crush\Nyour hopes, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504650,507695}You said that you had struck\Nanother layer 5 yards under,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:30.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507695,510322}but here you're digging\Nas deep as 20 yards, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510322,513117}Does your previous experience\Nreally apply here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:37.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513117,517788}There's a chance the usual layer distribution\Nis dislodged, and so is the coal…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:41.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517788,521125}Who is the geological\Nexpert here, lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521125,523627}Is it me or you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523627,524795}I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524795,526756}Sam! Sam. Sam…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:50.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526756,530801}Come on.\NLet's leave it to a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:55.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530801,535681}After all, he's a university professor\Narranged by Duke Radling himself, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535681,537516}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547443,548861}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553115,554617}Stop the car immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:15.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554992,555493}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555659,557953}Wait for me, Lassie! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563501,565211}Why did they stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565211,566253}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566879,568047}Is that your dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:29.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568589,569924}Huh? Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570841,572093}What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572093,573052}John Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573511,574762}So, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574762,577556}That's a fascinating, beautiful dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578933,580434}Thank you very much, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:42.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581060,582561}Do you really mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:46.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582561,586190}Yes. I like dogs very much,\Nand I know what I'm seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:49.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586190,589068}Especially her coat.\NIt is exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589068,591654}It's because I brush\Nher hair every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591654,594281}I see. I apologize for\Ninterrogating you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594281,595533}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595533,597785}I hope you can show your dog\Nclosely to me one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:58.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597785,598661}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:04.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600162,604834}I kind of like\Nwhen people praise you, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:10.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607795,610965}I understand where you're\Ncoming from, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610965,612842}Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613384,614885}Is Colin here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614885,616053}He's upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:16.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616053,616846}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:20.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617138,620266}Of course, I understand\Nif you can't pay immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:23.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620266,623561}but what about coal?\NDo you think you'll find new deposits?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:24.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623561,624979}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:27.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624979,627022}I don't know, and I can't\Ndo anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:29.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628566,629525}Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629525,631694}Was there any letter for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:33.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632194,633737}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633737,635197}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:37.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635197,637950}Let me guess, a letter\Nof appointment for a new job?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637950,639076}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639076,640202}No luck, as expected…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640995,642288}That was the third one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642288,643789}Don't lose hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:47.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643789,647168}I'm sure you'll find\Na good job sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647168,648335}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652631,653549}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657178,658637}What's up, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658637,660848}We think Spinner has already left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:01.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660848,661599}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:04.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661599,664393}But he said he didn't know\Nwhen that would be…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664393,667646}My Dad said that his father\Nsuddenly found a new job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667646,669565}It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669565,671984}I didn't even say goodbye to him…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:12.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671984,672985}Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:17.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673736,677656}No one had the chance\Nto say goodbye to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:18.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678115,678991}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:25.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679783,685372}Tell me that your dad won't get fired\Nand you and Lassie won't go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685372,686665}Of course they won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686665,688626}What are you even\Ntalking about, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689251,691420}I… I don't know.
Comment: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:34.25,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:694256,694256}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:43.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702723,703849}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709647,710856}Shutdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710856,713234}Is that all this man has to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:57.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713651,717947}He's already sent\Nhis report to the Duke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717947,720741}A report?\NAfter such a short survey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721075,724328}How can anyone decide something\Nso important, so lightly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724328,726247}What's he come here for, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726789,729291}I don't have the authority\Nto do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729291,730793}Please understand, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732670,734922}Sorry, but I simply can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734922,736465}Hey! Sam!\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736465,737925}To see the Duke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740552,741553}Sam…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745015,746350}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747101,748811}I won't authorize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748811,750396}But, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:34.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750396,754149}If you take a look at these historic records,\Nyou'll see that the Wellington Mine—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754149,756652}Comparing you and your records\Ngathered hastily in a single day
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:40.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756652,760030}and a scientist who has dedicated his life\Nto build his geologic knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760030,762366}who would you trust\Nas the decision maker?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765411,767621}I'm sorry, but I am very busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767913,769039}But, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:53.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769039,773627}How long do you want to deceive those men\Nhaving them work in a mine with no future?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774044,777631}Don't you see that they're better off\Nif the mine is shut down faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:01.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778090,781635}Rather than wasting money\Non prolonging a dubious investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:05.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781635,785639}isn't it better to use it to pay\Nthe miners their overdue salaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:09.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786307,789893}Answer me.\NWhat is the best decision here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:15.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791770,795691}By the way,\Nisn't your son's name John?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795691,796608}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:20.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796608,800446}As for this dog that is always with him,\Nisn't its name Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:21.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800446,801155}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801155,803699}It's a marvelous dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804074,805909}I happen to love dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:29.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805909,809580}My name is well-known\Namong collectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809580,810789}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:34.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810789,814001}If the mine gets closed,\Nyour family is going to need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:38.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814001,818213}Do you think you could\Nsell Lassie to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:44.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820215,824261}What will it be?\NDo you think we can make a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:47.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824720,827556}I am very sorry,\Nbut I absolutely can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:48.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827556,828599}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:51.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828599,831226}Lassie is my son's best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831226,832269}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833979,835898}What a peculiar fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835898,837232}Had he agreed to my offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:01.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837232,841278}I would've made Lassie the most\Nprized dog in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842321,844114}So are you going to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844656,846784}No, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846784,849995}But I think he made\Nsome really good points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849995,851163}Darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:851163,853665}Didn't you say that\Nwith a bit of patience,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853665,857211}you'd definitely find\Nnew coal deposits?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857211,859630}Yes. But, you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859630,861924}Since we came to this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861924,864218}you've been working for 15 years\Nat Wellington Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864218,867554}I remember the mess it was in\Nduring the Great Depression
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867554,870432}and all the problems\Nyou've preserved through thus far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870432,873477}Who's gotten the mine out of trouble\Nthese past 15 years, Sam Carraclough?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:35.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873477,875813}Well… It's because\Neveryone did their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876146,877689}Then what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:42.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878232,882194}You have to see it to the very end,\Nfor the sake of your colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883487,884363}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884363,885531}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:48.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885531,888158}We'll dig deeper\Nand collect more samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:48.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888158,888784}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888784,890202}That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905968,907302}Oh, it's you, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907302,908637}It's my Dad's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908637,909513}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909972,912015}Sam is down below\Nat the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:14.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:912433,914518}Down below? Dad is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915060,917354}Thanks to him,\NI can keep watch over the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917354,919857}I'm trying to do a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:21.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920190,921191}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924820,928824}Dad's been working in the depths\Nof the earth for long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:48.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943422,948093}Number 16, 24 inches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948093,949845}Number 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:53.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951472,953056}A clay rock, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953056,954766}This one is 8.5 inches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954766,956310}8.5 inches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:16:00.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956310,960355}Sam, don't lose to those\Nknow-it-all eggheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:05.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961023,965360}Not even the mine owner's powers\Ncan reach us down here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974036,975162}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976747,977748}He's finally fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978248,979249}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:22.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979791,982377}Thank you, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:40.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999520,1000771}How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:48.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004107,1008487}As expected,\Nhe won't trust amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015536,1016828}Listen, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:17:02.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016828,1022626}Looking at Dad, I started to wonder\Nif there's any way we could help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:04.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022626,1024169}I'm sure there's\Nsomething we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024169,1025087}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027756,1029091}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029091,1031552}I feel like I'm running away\Nwith my tail between my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032010,1033303}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033303,1036557}You decided to do it\Nto support your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:18.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037140,1038934}– Take care.\N– Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038934,1042104}Do your best, Hamilton,\Nwherever your travel takes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:22.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042104,1042896}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042896,1044314}We'll be on our way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044314,1045440}Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045440,1048193}Take care of yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048193,1049945}Godspeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:33.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051238,1053824}Lassie! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060664,1061665}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:46.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062874,1066545}I wonder who leaves next?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:50.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066545,1070299}This is us, who were working\Nin this mine since forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:54.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070299,1074386}If only the owner didn't turn\Na deaf ear to Sam's advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:03.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079725,1083437}Mr. Radling is\NPriscilla's grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1083437,1086898}He is the mustached man who\Npraised you the other day, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:11.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088483,1091403}We'll get him to change\Nhis mind, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:12.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091528,1092779}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:15.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092779,1095907}You came to show Lassie to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096199,1097701}Good. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:21.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097701,1101622}I know I keep saying this,\Nbut she is a truly magnificent dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101622,1103415}That's not why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111465,1114551}Interesting. I certainly understand\Nwhere you're coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114551,1115844}So…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:39.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115844,1119348}So you'll hear Dad out again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:43.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120182,1123769}Did your father ask you\Nto come here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124436,1125520}My father…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:47.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125520,1127064}No, that's all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127064,1129441}I didn't tell Dad that I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129441,1132944}It's just that when I look at him,\NI can't sit around doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:54.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133320,1134321}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:55.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134321,1135322}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135322,1137658}Listen to what my Dad has to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.65,0:18:58.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137658,1138492}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138492,1140077}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140077,1141745}Listen closely, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:07.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141745,1147292}I am not closing the mine in an effort\Nto make your lives miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:10.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147292,1150253}The chance that further survey\Nwill bring something is very slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:13.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150253,1153465}We cannot drag this out forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153465,1156093}These men have\Ntheir families to support.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:19.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156093,1159554}How is that?\NOr do you think I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160555,1163475}I'm glad you're a bright boy\Nwho understands the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:26.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163475,1166895}Please, sir, I'm begging you,\Nconduct the survey just one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:27.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166895,1167938}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169147,1170524}I can't allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.89,0:19:32.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170899,1172901}But if we do survey again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:36.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172901,1176947}we'll learn why the coal's exhausted\Nand we'll learn how to find more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:40.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176947,1180117}I don't have money\Nto organize such a survey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:43.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180117,1183745}I don't own a big mansion\Nor a car like you do, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:46.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183745,1186248}But if I only had all that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:49.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186248,1189960}I would do anything to keep\Nthe Wellington Coal Mine up and running!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:54.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190752,1194631}Do you understand the gravity\Nof what you are saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:55.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195048,1195632}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:57.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196508,1197134}The gravity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:03.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199302,1203515}What you are talking about\Nis a serious and important subject
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203515,1205642}that decides\Nthe fate of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207686,1209813}I know all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:17.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211440,1217696}If so, your words must be accompanied\Nby a corresponding sense of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:22.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217696,1222451}This mansion, the servants.\NThe countless companies that I run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222451,1225454}They're all very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:27.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225454,1227497}I'm responsible for all of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227497,1230375}In matters such as the decision\Nwhether to close the mine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:35.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230375,1235547}there is simply no place for gambling.\NIt is far too important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235547,1236757}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236757,1239885}But there are times\Nwhen you have to gamble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240427,1241762}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:45.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241762,1245807}Let me ask you a question.\NWhat is the most precious thing to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246600,1247601}Err…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:53.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249269,1253064}Let's take your thinking\Nfor a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:56.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253064,1256234}I believe it is safe to assume\Nthat Lassie is very valuable to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:21:00.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256234,1260781}Would you be ready to gamble her\Nfor the success of the mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263158,1264618}Gamble Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264618,1266328}See? You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:09.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268330,1269706}There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:11.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270290,1271082}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:13.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271082,1273752}As my Dad said, we will…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273752,1275253}We will…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275253,1277964}We'll strike another deposit soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:29.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284346,1289768}I admire your determination.\NRest assured, I will keep my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:31.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290894,1291978}Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291978,1294940}We will…\NWe will find more coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:35.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294940,1295649}Until then…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296650,1298985}Until then, please wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299986,1301822}Be patient.
Comment: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:57.37,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1317379,1317379}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:03.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320715,1323385}{\i1}Dad, tell me that\Nwe'll find more coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.38,0:22:04.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1323385,1324886}{\i1}I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.88,0:22:06.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324886,1326680}{\i1}I'll help everyone with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:10.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326680,1330892}{\i1}Otherwise they'll take\NLassie to Scotland!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:14.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330892,1334229}{\i1}Next episode:\N"Do Your Best, John! Protect Lassie".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:15.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334229,1335647}{\i1}Be sure to watch!
